<br />
<br /><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NH1A4qvCl4s" class="postlink">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NH1A4qvCl4s</a>
<br />
<br />Screenshot is of the 32-bit linux version running in KDE, but it also can be compiled and ran on 64-bit linux, 32 and 64-bit windows, and intel based macs.

		

